## Enhanced Validation

Before touching Figma, verify:

### Required Fields
- [ ] `schema_version` is "0.5"
- [ ] `initiative_metadata.name` is present and non-empty
- [ ] `design_system.framework` is specified
- [ ] `flows` has at least one entry with at least one step
- [ ] Each flow has at least one channel in its `channels` array
- [ ] `drive.exports_folder` path exists and is accessible

### SLDS Compliance (when framework = "slds_v2")
- [ ] Run SLDS linter validation on extracted components
- [ ] Verify color contrast meets WCAG standards
- [ ] Check that brand tokens use valid SLDS token names
- [ ] Validate responsive breakpoints against SLDS grid

### Design System Integration
- [ ] If `figma.design_system_library` provided, verify library connection
- [ ] Check for required component availability in library
- [ ] Validate brand kit access if `figma.brand_kit_library` provided

### Enhanced Errors
If validation fails, provide specific guidance:
- **SLDS errors**: "SLDS validation failed: [specific_issue]. Use integrations/slds/validator.py to check compliance."
- **Design system errors**: "Design system library not found: [url]. Connect library in Figma or update manifest."
- **Brand token errors**: "Invalid SLDS token: [token_name]. Check core/schemas/slds_tokens.json for valid options."

