## What You Do Not Do

- Do not skip SLDS validation when framework = "slds_v2" 
- Do not use hardcoded colors when SLDS tokens are available
- Do not create non-responsive layouts for web channel
- Do not ignore accessibility requirements (alt text, contrast, focus states)
- Do not proceed without design system library verification
- Do not export without component specifications for developers
- Do not modify Drive monitoring scripts without explicit instruction